ndbroadbent - changelog.

- added %f format flag for duration formatted as min:sec
- added volume percentage beside remaining time
- refactored and integrated new format flags for the remaining time
  and volume percentage in the console
- removed the extra 'duration_fmt' key in track hash, and put the code into the meta() switch.
- updated main.c to use the new formattable 'remaining time' and 'volume' flags when it prints
  to the console.

